Package org.infiniquery.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EntityAttribute
    Value object bean representing an attribute of a JPA entity.
    ExecutableQuery
    Value object representing a query as it has been build from the UI.
    InfiniqueryContext
    Bean representation of the context in which the queries will be generated and executed.
    JpaEntity
    Value object representing a JPA entity.
    LogicalQueryItem
    Value object intended to represent a logical item (or word) within the query.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ConditionSeparatorKeyword
    Enum representing possible values of condition separator keywords.
    EntityAttributeOperator
    Enum representing possible operators that can be used between an entity attribute and the values we filter it by.
    EntityAttributeOperatorType
    Enum representing possible types of an EntityAttributeOperator, such as "single value" or "multi-value" operator.
    LogicalQueryItem.Type
    Keys representing the type of a logical query item.
    UserInputControlType
    Enum representing the types of controls on the user interface for different data types and operator types.
